parameters:
Bunny-chan: Alright, tonight marks the start of Monster
Fight!! This time, uh... it's a special match between the
Shark Duke and the Mayor! That... ah, eek, trembling...
Spectator: Get lost, Orca jerk! Don't scare Bunny-chan!!

Spectator: The enemy of all citizens isn't welcome here!
Boo! Boo!!

Orca Mayor: These lower-class citizens are so noisy! Maybe I
should raise your taxes?

Memimi: (To think the Mayor would threaten the citizens...
This guy, everything he does is irritating...! He's an
unforgivable man!!)

Memimi: (I absolutely can't lose to someone like him! I
don't want to appear in an adult video no matter what... I
must defeat him with all my strength...!)

Bunny-chan: T-the match will start in 10 seconds. Please get
to your starting positions! Oh... I'm scared...
